               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Image of the Trinity, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="38v" facs="005">Fols 1r–38v</locus>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas">Sayfa Śǝllāse</title>
                     <note>Arranged for days of the week</note>


                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                       <locus from="1r" to="5r" facs="005">Fols 1r–5r</locus>
                       <title>Introduction, intended for Monday (?, not so marked).</title>

                         <msItem xml:id="msi_i1.1.1">
                           <locus from="1r" facs="005">Fols 1r and following</locus>
                           <title>The prayer to the Trinity, “I take refuge”, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተማኅፀንኩ፡</foreign></title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1r" facs="005">Fol. 1r</locus>በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>፩አምላክ፡ እነቅህ፡ ወእትነሣእ፡ በቅድስት፡ ሥላሴ፡ እንዘ፡ አአምን፡ ወእትመኃፀን፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አሜን፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                           <locus target="#2r" facs="006">2r</locus>ሰላም፡ ለአብ፡ ነቅአ፡ ዘይት፡ ምህረተ፡ ጥሉል፡ ሰላም፡ ለወልድ፡ ነቅአ፡ ዘይተ፡ ምህረት፡ ጥሉል፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                           </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.2">
                           <locus from="4v" facs="009">Fols 4v and following</locus>
                           <title>Miracle of the Trinity</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በረከተ፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አሜን፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ አተዉ፡ ውስተ፡ ገጸ፡ አርያም፡ አብኒ፡ ይቤ፡ ወሀለውኒ፡ ይቤ፡ ጊዜ፡ ይመጽእ፡ ቃልየ፡ ወይትሌአል፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                       <locus from="5v" to="7v" facs="010">Fols 5v–7v</locus>
                       <title>Tuesday</title>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                           <locus from="5v" facs="010">Fols 5v and following</locus>
                           <title>Prayer</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">አሐትም፡ ፍጽምየ፡ በመለኮተ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐትም፡ ከዋላየ፡ በመለኮተ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                           <locus from="6v" facs="011">Fols 6v and following</locus>
                          <title>Miracle</title>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አሜን፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ በፈለገ፡ ጸቃውዕ፡</incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                       <locus from="7v" to="11v" facs="012">Fols 7v–11v</locus>
                       <title>Wednesday</title>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                           <locus from="7v" facs="011">Fols 7v and following</locus>
                           <title>Prayer</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ህቡረ፡ ሀሎ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                           <locus from="11r" facs="015">Fols 11r and following</locus>
                           <title>Miracle</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አሜን፡ ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                       <locus from="11v" to="17r" facs="016">Fols 11v–17r</locus>
                       <title>Thursday</title>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.1">
                           <locus from="11v" facs="016">Fols 11v and following</locus>
                           <title>Prayer</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩በግጻዌ፡ ሥሉስ፡ በሥላሴ፡ ግጽው፡ ሳህድ፡ አምላክ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.2">
                           <locus from="16v" facs="021">Fols 16v and following</locus>
                           <title>Miracle</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አሜን፡ ወሀሎ፡ ፩መኰንን፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡ ወአሐተ፡ አዘዘ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡ ሠራዊቱ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                         </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                         <locus from="17r" to="23v" facs="021">Fols 17r–23v</locus>
                         <title>Friday</title>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.1">
                           <title>Prayer</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                             <locus from="17r" facs="021">Fols 17r and following</locus>አይ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአይ፡ ከናፍር፡ ዘይክል፡ ነቢበ፡ ዕበየ፡ ግንሮሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/><locus from="19r" facs="023">19r and following</locus>ስብሐት፡ ለሥላሴ፡ ፈጣሪየ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለሥላሴ፡ ንጉሥየ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                           </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.2">
                           <locus from="23r" facs="027">Fols 23r and following</locus>
                           <title>Miracle</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ወ፡ አይ፡ ከናፍር፡ ወአይ። ልቡና፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አሜን፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወአግረሩ፡ ላዕለ፡ መንበሮሙ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                         </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                         <locus from="23v" to="27r" facs="028">Fols 23v–27r</locus>
                         <title>Saturday</title>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6.1">
                           <locus from="23v" facs="028">Fols 23v and following</locus>
                           <title><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2933RepCh214">Malkǝʾ-hymn to the
                                                  Holy Trinity</title></title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለፍቅር፡ መለኮት፡ በትስብእቱ፡ ዘጾመ፡ እንበይነ፡ ዘ[አ]ርአያሁ፡ ከመ፡ የሀበነ፡ ሰላም፡ ለፍቅረ፡ መለኮት፡ ዘይጼአን፡ ላዕለ፡ ሰረገላ፡ ኪሩቤል፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                         </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                         <locus from="27r" to="33v" facs="031">Fols 27r–33v</locus>
                         <title>Sunday</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang="gez">አኀሥሥ፡ ጽድቀ፡ ዘእምኀቤከ፡ ኦቀመረ፡ ጽድቅ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                         <locus from="33v" to="38v" facs="038">Fols 33v–38v</locus>
                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2736RepCh20">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Śǝllāse</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለህላዌክሙ፡ ዘይመውዕ፡ ህላውያተ። ለረኪበ፡ ስሙ፡ ኅቡዕ፡ አመ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ተምኔተ።</incipit>
                       </msItem>

